<br />\n大概這間不過是 為 ranking 得學店吧<br />\nShitty 染紅很弱智 為人民幣去<br />\n遺忘校訓 唔會真摯<br />\n<br />\n城大各位 找郭位 考入去都曬學費<br />\n願和你 頂硬靠著手足守望跟勉勵<br />\n槍炮裡完成學位 守信念代價真貴<br />\n校董怎會助你爭訴求 巴之閉<br />\n<br />\n又中 TG 死咁滯 橡膠會射爛個胃<br />\n拉咗佢唔幫住你 運程能預計<br />\n未能入世 就已乞米<br />\n<br />\n城大各位 找郭位 考入去都曬學費<br />\n沒材幹 喺校舍內四方起牆的契弟<br />\nGrad 咗費事行大禮 宿舍會自我關閉<br />\n綠衫狗會直接衝入嚟 真失禮<br />\n<br />\n城大各位 找郭位 考入去都曬學費<br />\n沒材幹 喺校舍內四方起牆的契弟<br />\nGrad 咗費事行大禮 宿舍會自我關閉<br />\n綠衫狗會直接衝入嚟 真失禮"},{"pid":"2e395663e4e48726164b4dd075672816a8f11649","tid":1744984,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T04:15:36.000Z","msg":"原 Post:<br />\n<br />\n城大各位    找郭位    考入去都曬學費<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1742643\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1742643</a>"},{"pid":"4be22edb5a42b5988a74585c54fef2a778bd473c","tid":1744984,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T04:16:19.000Z","msg":"多謝 IAMGROOOOT 巴打幫手錄音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"681c6e362fdfa37c2cd1f4e7c4920ff242f46143","tid":1744984,"uid":316537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T04:19:51.000Z","msg":"癡線笑死"},{"pid":"49fb8740cb76d9ae0bd36b909913c610114c0c3e","tid":1744984,"uid":77556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T04:20:43.000Z","msg":"等睇nvm 擋子彈巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deb89fb16f81208e512cd0d5b68f105d290625f1","tid":1744984,"uid":236171,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T04:20:50.000Z","msg":"知道城大仔因為班校長/校董嘅關係<br />\n參與抗爭都比部份 U 難、辛苦<br />\n<br />\n送翻首歌俾你哋打氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>City 仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span>"},